snippet.title: Moving Out Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Take couch co-op to a whole new level when Moving Out comes to Nintendo Switch, PS4, Xbox One and PC on April 28th 2020.

Wishlist now on Steam: http://bit.ly/MovingOutSteam

In Moving Out, you’ll be relocating furnishings in increasingly bizarre locations in a fast-paced furniture moving simulator! Customise your character and play with up to three friends locally!

Learn more: http://bit.ly/MovingOutReleaseDate

Official website: http://bit.ly/MovingOutGame
Follow Moving Out on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MovingOutGame
Follow Moving Out on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MovingOutGame
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/


About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Aven Colony, The Escapists, Genesis Alpha One, Overcooked, Sword Legacy: Omen, Yoku’s Island Express, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
